# FILE DESCRIPTION																															
# Pa, Pb, Aa, Ab, ma, mb = tree growth parameters (Perin et al.)
# v1, v2, v3, v4 = parameter of stem volume equation (VC22tige) of Dagnelie et al.
# vb1, vb2, vb3, vb4 = parameter of branch volume equation (VC22branche) of Dagnelie et al.
# vlog = parameter used to estimate the volume of high-value log -- volume of one log = (vstem + vbranch)/vlog

#mortality_c_130_treshold : set to 1000 for now. If the mortality model is efficient, mortality_c_130_treshold is not necessary																															


# hd1, hd2, hd3, hd4 = parameters of the allometric H-D relationships fitted by Dagnelie et al.
# Color: color used to display this species r,g,b in [0,255]																															
